You must coordinate with the florist to deliver the centerpieces early on the day of the event. Inspect every arrangement to ensure they meet our quality standards before display.
I am putting you in charge of the coat check area. Make sure you organize the hangers efficiently and provide each guest with a claim ticket for their items.
